+    /* patch 0043 (fattorino): async RAM page-in of the experts promoted THIS
+     * scan so their first decode load hits page cache, not a cold SSD read.
+     * OFF (DS4_REAP_PREFETCH_DELTA unset) => promo_n==0 path never taken. */
